            <lg xml:id="TK149">
<l>nalakkuriyār yāreṉi ṉāmanīr vaippiṟ</l>
<l>piṟaṟkuriyā ṭōṭōyā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who has a right to happiness? They who in this world with fearsome waters</l>
<l>have never touched the shoulder of her who's rightfully another's.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
